28-7e4f-5ce3-bf62-373400a8a46a","timeToRead":12}},{"node":{"id":"ca3cc4cf-0ddf-5fb3-a58d-2354b2f0a10e","timeToRead":5}},{"node":{"id":"fe7fd5be-04af-5d1a-b969-f8f4de7db655","timeToRead":1}},{"node":{"id":"fb3bc99d-cf2f-5fbd-981d-1d701815f87b","timeToRead":66}},{"node":{"id":"4de1fb79-73c7-5593-adc3-427351c465e9","timeToRead":101}},{"node":{"id":"9a102758-e412-5f31-8753-54534e8fdb15","timeToRead":1}},{"node":{"id":"a07217e5-4cbe-54e4-9566-2a0df732a1a4","timeToRead":1}},{"node":{"id":"c8a73065-3214-5616-93f3-0df2a119e91d","timeToRead":1}}]},"markdownRemark":{"id":"a40d34f8-b202-5f5b-8c33-19c7c163bbce","excerpt":"同步链接: https://www.shanejix.com/posts/小米手机欧版 MIUI 通用卡刷教程/ 各种原因，把备用机 MI6 刷成欧版 MIUI…","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>同步链接: <a href=\"https://www.shanejix.com/posts/%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E6%AC%A7%E7%89%88MIUI%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%8D%A1%E5%88%B7%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/\">https://www.shanejix.com/posts/小米手机欧版 MIUI 通用卡刷教程/</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>各种原因，把备用机 MI6 刷成欧版 MIUI，大致流程差不多，记录下方便后续查阅</p>\n<p>大致步骤如下：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"typescript\"><pre class=\"language-typescript\"><code class=\"language-typescript\">数据备份 <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> 解锁 <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> 刷入Recover <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> 刷入<span class=\"token constant\">ROM</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> 跳过Google验证</code></pre></div>\n<h2>数据备份</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>数据是无价的！数据是无价的！数据是无价的！</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>手机变砖无所谓，重要数据一定要备份，诸如：照片，聊天记录，文档等</p>\n<p>备份数据可以直接使用小米官方的工具（功能很多自行研究）：<a href=\"http://zhushou.xiaomi.com/\">小米手机助手</a></p>\n<p>具体步骤：</p>\n<p>一，打开 开发者模式</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\">设置 -> 我的设备 -> 全部参数 -> MIUI 版本（一直点）</code></pre></div>\n<p>二，开启 USB 调试</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\">设置 -> 更多设置 -> 开发者选项 -> USB 调试</code></pre></div>\n<p>三，下载 小米手机助手 并安装</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\">http://zhushou.xiaomi.com/</code></pre></div>\n<p>四，手机 USB 连接电脑</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\">使用小米手机助手备份/恢复重要数据</code></pre></div>\n<p>不得不吐槽下即使是官方的工具，依然有 bug</p>\n<h2>解锁</h2>\n<p>第二步坑就不少了，新手机限制 7 天能解锁！MI0LIteZoom 使用快一年，解锁依然有 7 天限制，各种方法绕不过。最后等了 10 多天才解锁成功，恶心的不行！</p>\n<p>准备如下：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"token list punctuation\">-</span> 小米账号（已有解锁权限，并且是当前设备登录的账号）\n\n<span class=\"token list punctuation\">-</span> 小米解锁助手</code></pre></div>\n<p>具体步骤：</p>\n<p>一，绑定账号和关闭服务</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"token list punctuation\">-</span> 建议登出 Google 账号，不然后续可能跳不过 Google 验证\n\n<span class=\"token list punctuation\">-</span> 登录常用的 小米账号 （注意：和后续解锁工具中的登录的账号保持一直）\n\n<span class=\"token list punctuation\">-</span> 关闭查找设备功能</code></pre></div>\n<p>二，申请解锁权限</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\">进入 http://www.miui.com/unlock/ 登录 小米账号 申请解锁</code></pre></div>\n<p>三，下载解锁助手</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\">进入 https://en.miui.com/unlock/download_en.html 下载并安装</code></pre></div>\n<p>四，解锁</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"token list punctuation\">1.</span> 打开小米解锁助手，并登录小米账号\n\n<span class=\"token list punctuation\">2.</span> 手机关机后，使手机进入 Fastboot 模式（同时按住 电源键 + 音量下）\n\n<span class=\"token list punctuation\">3.</span> 查看小米解锁工具是否读取到设备\n\n<span class=\"token list punctuation\">4.</span> 点解 解锁（unlock）按钮</code></pre></div>\n<p>解锁成功后，手机回重启 开机界面回出现 unlocked 标志</p>\n<h2>刷入 Recovery</h2>\n<p>终于进入正题了，准备如下：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"token list punctuation\">-</span> ADB SDK\n\n<span class=\"token list punctuation\">-</span> TWRP 镜像</code></pre></div>\n<p>具体步骤：</p>\n<p>一，下载 ADB（Android Debug Bridge） SDK</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\">打开 https://developer.android.google.cn/studio/releases/platform-tools 选择对应系统版本下载并解压\n\n<span class=\"token list punctuation\">-</span> 该工具能够在连接的安卓设备上运行命令</code></pre></div>\n<p>二，下载 TWRP</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\">打开 https://androidfilehost.com/?a=show&amp;w=files&amp;flid=318170 （官方定制 TWRP，支持 OTA 更新），没有则使用 https://twrp.me/Devices/Xiaomi 下载对应手机型号的 img 文件\n\n<span class=\"token list punctuation\">-</span> 注意：每台手机都要一个别称，例如 MI6(sagit)，找到自己手机的别称</code></pre></div>\n<p>三，刷入 TWRP</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\">将下载的 TWRP 镜像 移动到 adb.exe 等文件的同一目录下</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\">手机进入到 Fastboot 模式（开机同时按住电源键和下音量键）</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\">手机用 USB 数据线连接电脑</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\">在 adb.exe 所在目录，按住 shift 并右键，点击在此处打开 Powershell 窗口 / 在此处打开 CMD 窗口</code></pre></div>\n<p>依次运行如下命令</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">fastboot.exe flash recovery twrp.img // twrp.img 需要替换成你下载的镜像文件的路径\n\nfastboot.exe boot twrp.img // twrp.img 需要替换成你下载的镜像文件的路径</code></pre></div>\n<p>如果不生效，则依次执行</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">./fastboot.exe flash recovery twrp.img // twrp.img 需要替换成你下载的镜像文件的路径\n\n./fastboot.exe boot twrp.img // twrp.img 需要替换成你下载的镜像文件的路径</code></pre></div>\n<h2>刷入 ROM</h2>\n<p>重头戏，具体步骤：</p>\n<p>一，下载 ROM</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\">进入 https://xiaomi.eu/community/ 获取对应版本 ROM 并下载</code></pre></div>\n<p>二，双清</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"token list punctuation\">-</span> 进入 Recovery （开机同时按住音量加 + 开机键）\n\n<span class=\"token list punctuation\">-</span> 点 Wipe ，勾选 system, cache, data 然后滑动进行清除</code></pre></div>\n<p>三，传入 ROM</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"token list punctuation\">-</span> 在 Recovery 模式传入下载的 ROM 包\n\n<span class=\"token list punctuation\">-</span> 如果传输失败，则重新挂载（在 TWRP 工具主界面点 Mount 然后点 Enable MTP），重新连接电脑</code></pre></div>\n<p>四，Install</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\">点击 Install ，刷机完成，重启</code></pre></div>\n<h2>跳过 Google 验证</h2>\n<p>概率问题，不能对症下药，多尝试，有如下方法：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"token list punctuation\">1.</span> 开机不连 WiFi，长按关机键进入飞行模式</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"token list punctuation\">2.</span> 拔出手机卡重启手机</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"token list punctuation\">3.</span> xx 上网</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"token list punctuation\">4.</span> 刷机前登出 Google 账号</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token number\">5</span>. ADB\n\n// 在 Recovery 终端中操作\n\nadb shell settings put secure user_setup_complete <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\nadb shell settings put global device_provisioned <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\nadb <span class=\"token function\">reboot</span>\n\n// 或者\n\n./adb shell settings put secure user_setup_complete <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n./adb shell settings put global device_provisioned <span class=\"token number\">1</span>\n./adb <span class=\"token function\">reboot</span>\n\n// 上面不行则\n\n<span class=\"token function\">dd</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">if</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>/dev/zero <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">of</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>/dev/block/bootdevice/by-name/frp</code></pre></div>\n<p>方法 2 和方法 5 都成功过，方法 5 是刷机前没有登出 Google 账号</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>作者：<a href=\"https://www.shanejix.com/\">shanejix</a>\n出处：<a href=\"https://www.shanejix.com/posts/%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E6%AC%A7%E7%89%88MIUI%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%E5%8D%A1%E5%88%B7%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/\">https://www.shanejix.com/posts/小米手机欧版 MIUI 通用卡刷教程/</a>\n版权：本作品采用<a href=\"http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0/\">「署名-非商业性使用-相同方式共享 4.0 国际」</a>许可协议进行许可。\n声明：转载请注明出处！</p>\n</blockquote>","frontmatter":{"title":"小米手机欧版MIUI通用卡刷教程","date":"January 12, 2022","update":"April 12, 2022","url":"https://github.com/shanejix/shanejix.github.io/issues/89"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/小米手机欧版MIUI通用卡刷教程/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/[Snippet] - Axios download file stream and write file in Node/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[Snippet] - Axios download file stream and write file in Node","tags":["Node","Snippet","Axios"]}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/JavaScript Event Loop in Browser/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"JavaScript Event Loop in Browser","tags":["JavaScript","Node","Browser"]}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3159585216","63159454"]}